  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c5b17e42-fb7e-4925-aef7-4c0803109ab0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a50f43a8-5b7a-4114-9bf2-523f598960a5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-2ed64c41-64e2-4b75-8a9f-bea2d52995ea\">안녕하세요 몸과 마음을 건강하게!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7bc41887-2adb-4d53-9929-00cbc0f2c19d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system se-weight-unset  \" id=\"SE-323f99c9-e5f0-430f-9442-9532d8e251e6\">이수한의원 입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c5b17e42-fb7e-4925-aef7-4c0803109ab0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ccbfb50-ec1c-4b35-a5d3-b5dad8e62736\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"1\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_1.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ec51ad1e-809a-44f0-a37f-41da461f2855\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e1470ec8-24d2-4bea-8552-3b90bc124c4c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-017c306e-38ec-4948-9f65-0942b065cd8f\"><b>– 혈액이 막히면 몸도, 마음도 막힙니다 –</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-085439fc-8256-40b2-bcb8-7b67cd53fd15\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cf5efa34-e25a-46a4-9951-a44052642a74\">우리가 흔히 &quot;혈이 잘 안 돈다&quot;는 말을 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cd68b727-cea4-43ec-bf7f-e2fd0ed61f29\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3347182e-7c45-4d94-85ab-d63555752eae\">그런데 이 말은 단순한 느낌이 아니라 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-03e13f8e-a72f-4062-965d-1ba8464e423c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d7bfc9e4-3f3c-4d11-adb1-7dbeb2f81861\">실제 건강에 아주 중요한 의미를 담고 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff320a4a-8146-4eec-8434-849de53fef3e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7fe26d87-4f18-4e95-8d1c-0c48f22aa256\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d58d8076-ae27-4a8e-950d-411506703daf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-623358d0-9e3d-41d2-895f-013e00d28cfc\">혈액순환이란 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-73611895-8740-4e14-9ff3-d699efd95fa5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f66cb8eb-5c6c-4546-bac5-831ef8320c6f\">말 그대로 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-56293751-ad77-43f3-9dba-5ecbc6df042a\"><b>심장에서 내보낸 피가 온몸을 돌고 다시 돌아오는 과정</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7fda30cc-bf05-4dca-944a-c8fbc0b4d863\">인데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6ddd2128-6865-4e82-a2fc-1aaeab60f4be\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ada6a62b-9937-4a92-a690-9f431744a3c2\">이 과정이 원활하지 않으면 다양한 증상이 나타납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ec51ad1e-809a-44f0-a37f-41da461f2855\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-ff5edb4b-fa68-4246-9bf2-767f2c4d713a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4483bd61-a02f-45fb-a406-d70268ba59a6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4483bd61-a02f-45fb-a406-d70268ba59a6\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/974054353940ae09.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1700\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/974054353940ae09.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/974054353940ae09.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-4483bd61-a02f-45fb-a406-d70268ba59a6\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5cc76a16-d068-4b2b-aca4-b1b4175ccced\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-800098c0-7241-4cad-af5b-0121b08e819e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-55f400b8-008b-486c-a425-ef7f52e05853\"><b>❗혈액순환이 안 될 때 나타나는 증상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4abc9098-4dc3-484d-88af-da367b095233\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-51d58f5e-8dca-4edf-b4e8-773705b83398\"><b>손발 저림</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0bca19d4-fdfa-45dc-ab48-74d1c392a0ce\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-47ecd319-8339-4e6d-a71c-8e81abea461a\">특히 앉았다 일어날 때 찌릿하거나 저리는 증상은 말초 혈액순환 문제일 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a0d59bc-2611-4143-bf1d-291664066bd7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-08957730-a5b1-431a-b06d-3845c0bbaed0\">수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eab31545-e55c-4932-bc73-613e49ea42d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0080ef17-823f-4710-83f4-21291df6b23f\"><b>만성 피로</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c6c2cc2b-bf95-498e-934b-e47f45abe5a4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8c63fa20-5709-4200-b833-c708e8edd14a\">혈액이 제대로 돌지 않으면 산소와 영양소 공급이 부족해져 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cce47b93-b0f6-42bd-ba47-5d35ddf3d803\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f47e362c-e4b5-4f57-9b8f-41208d3a4aa5\">쉽게 피곤해집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-afe690fa-d8c0-46a0-9a17-b76f764cbf8b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b0e658da-1f37-49b1-b91b-33ea051facd4\"><b>두통, 어지럼증</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e562cf58-5363-416f-b06d-b82883755cfb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-46595347-7faf-4426-97ad-5b30cf09334c\">뇌로 가는 혈류가 원활하지 않으면 머리가 무겁거나 아플 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c90b942e-3709-4976-a5c8-d6702f717840\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e8421c54-287b-4fad-9640-02d35c87b4f8\"><b>냉증</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7aed69da-827e-43f4-a5e5-79dc7a25e0b2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c1195506-3a8a-45d6-98fc-cf924622d60c\">특히 여성분들 중 손발이 항상 차가운 경우가 많은데, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-45b5f80a-9911-4c48-8fdf-a58fb61e1b61\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c7788b5e-300a-4993-ae0c-45014fe4a1e2\">이는 말초혈관으로 피가 잘 가지 않는 상태입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfb1a88b-ea20-4658-8d34-6f0a7a35b14a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ba5784fd-202a-499b-a833-358e79e72c4d\"><b>소화불량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-892fb105-04a8-4827-ab99-c164b0e5cf07\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1bd40a09-34c1-4460-93ff-5516208c92c3\">장기에도 피가 충분히 공급되지 않으면 소화기능이 떨어질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83e650c4-85d6-4e83-9c67-40741f21ec2a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-81a552df-6e6b-496a-ae9a-9f087ee30be4\"><b>집중력 저하, 기억력 저하</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-db7c6db7-60a5-45ba-8422-e05b75d9b2c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-210f2c62-6fec-4591-b62e-369e6aa7fe2d\">뇌 혈류가 부족하면 인지기능도 영향을 받을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5cc76a16-d068-4b2b-aca4-b1b4175ccced\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-55058ca9-c115-4fb8-88ed-cb77d5a82a86\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-89a5c42f-91a1-473e-8d6d-be844e45e75a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9c2d7742-617e-4c61-8178-f9574c48ac3f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8e9af096-d93e-4e67-a421-416d9df2b88f\"><b>🌿 한의학에서 말하는 혈액순환</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e2f81487-3ada-4524-bb70-044a3e68b134\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1327af68-0074-44b8-be94-64b3ca19e9a9\">한의학에서는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-995cfcd9-268e-4d4e-b24c-6e9720f54454\"><b>‘기혈(氣血)’의 흐름</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-94c75b21-ae69-496a-81a5-6d97c7462489\">이 원활해야 건강하다고 봅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-abae4148-a67c-4bf6-a8a8-8dd828ee27c2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6d2090a7-ed9b-4b3f-bf23-85bdd6bb2df2\">이 중에서도 &#x27;혈(血)&#x27;이 막히는 것을 어혈(瘀血)이라고 하며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8bfb042f-7346-4d3f-bde6-c2eab2978edc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ae0045fc-54a7-4a7d-9917-985af4f2d174\">이는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c744c09a-83a0-44f3-bffd-1f21dc4c1a4d\"><b>통증, 냉증, 월경불순, 만성질환 등</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-518c134d-1fb4-44c4-aa0d-1d547857b092\">을 유발할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f155a06e-b380-4760-aed2-e419076e0bbf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b67dc3d1-4db1-4662-80a2-75df7e1bb911\">한의학적으로 혈액순환을 개선하기 위해 아래와 같은 방법들이 사용됩니다:</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-89a5c42f-91a1-473e-8d6d-be844e45e75a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fb40cd2f-5d90-465f-b547-56f99113d4cf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fb40cd2f-5d90-465f-b547-56f99113d4cf\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ea9eac6e55cd66.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ea9eac6e55cd66.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/12ea9eac6e55cd66.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"750\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-fb40cd2f-5d90-465f-b547-56f99113d4cf\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-06dd67bf-bf4c-4c74-b57b-43b9048fa798\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4c4a7fa-89fb-4556-b04c-5de8f46a27f7\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bafdadf5-2aee-4a24-a103-a2712f5d5f64\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e3e3adda-1fed-4daf-8724-280b89fa5598\"><b>✔ 한의학적 혈액순환 개선 방법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-574d277c-4b3c-444c-9e5f-2ed2ee8ca6a2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8b951965-8a37-4d7e-9083-79690457fa6d\"><b>한약 복용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a5dbaad-fa0d-4faf-8e67-b7d232fdecc2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e0ba6f32-9275-4515-be24-4a2fb7c0f28d\">어혈을 풀고 기혈 순환을 도와주는 한약(예: 궁귀조혈음, 당귀작약산 등)은 개인 체질에 맞게 처방됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6896cd90-8d20-4ea9-bc6c-dc51a38f9047\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4b6b188c-9af2-4cac-a893-44f36b84dbde\"><b>침 치료</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-651a5414-e9f6-46d5-bbb7-b098391717f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-383d18c6-8d07-45f0-bbbd-ba89605a35e5\">경혈(經穴)을 자극해 기혈이 잘 흐르도록 도와주며, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fa853797-731e-4e54-b9ee-18a08f7bc39b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-89ec4413-8196-4c9b-af8e-b8d93fe66b23\">특정 부위의 순환 개선에 효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20e9710e-7994-4278-b589-69277d2a0ff5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-95e2e72e-9d88-4731-8a00-15278148a351\"><b>뜸 치료(온열요법)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a92e675-64c3-4883-9c8b-f4e5c9ac40e3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ccd887db-762c-4cdd-a041-2f54782f0183\">몸을 따뜻하게 하고 혈관을 확장시켜 혈류를 좋게 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d4bd65e-d634-4b2f-a413-949b1c4959d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1f231ccb-a06a-4649-82d9-07ced2b5d905\">특히 냉증과 생리통에 효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-87da7d37-844a-46f5-8d2e-5fe4e92db578\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b16a9105-0d99-4468-b8c7-8837940eea66\"><b>약침 요법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1e6c987e-7285-4ea7-80b8-1eda2cbe9331\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-81ed3ada-6946-48f9-835d-e098609daff2\">한약 성분을 직접 경혈에 주입해 빠른 순환개선 효과를 노리는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-13858512-d30e-477b-8e4c-676210a15f88\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f622345f-7eed-451c-9528-bd719210a557\">치료법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-afc8e789-b935-465e-a132-ca2973ffdcd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8118e2cf-ac76-44fd-ab58-9ffe906b7e34\"><b>생활습관 관리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da91556a-abeb-48cb-aba3-bd8bfc47172a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0c716920-4600-4722-b9fb-17bcf09d272f\">기름지고 자극적인 음식은 피하고, 충분한 수분 섭취와 꾸준한 스트레칭, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e998ef6-d0ba-4268-b2be-39797ae0a28c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-836fe2f8-508d-4e63-8645-0c2d9bf52506\">반신욕도 추천됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f4c4a7fa-89fb-4556-b04c-5de8f46a27f7\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-062b1eed-bc52-4807-a8f6-81c67e6350d8\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_video\", \"id\" :\"SE-062b1eed-bc52-4807-a8f6-81c67e6350d8\", \"data\" : { \"videoType\" : \"player\", \"vid\" : \"21F891F7E3A55DE97B8BC2262953FCCA04AD\", \"inkey\" : \"V1299b2280c640d9f0f1dda18bcd7e